title: What If? Collection (1977-2013)
description:
What If? is an experiment: take a significant event in the Marvel Universe and speculate about what might have happened if it had had a different outcome. Each issue offers a look at characters we know in situations they might never really face. Each story takes place in a separate reality that doesn't affect the central continuity, so there are no rules and no limits. Characters can die--and often do.


Credit to Scanners!
